{"tid":1024547,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭斯指華為5G設備構成威脅　楊潔篪即場反駁","createTime":"2019-02-16T15:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T17:10:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca605c7d609bffcd52e5ef1b62e0148a072dff0","tid":1024547,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T15:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190216/s00005/a4c7d4bca9489953f7ef6f369fe98446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190216%2Fs00005%2Fa4c7d4bca9489953f7ef6f369fe98446.jpg&h=629971b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯在周六（16日）的慕尼黑安全會議（Munich Security Conference）發言，指華為5G設備構成「威脅」，為北京提供重要安全設備，進入通訊網絡以獲取數據。中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任楊潔篪同場反駁，指美方的指控只是出於自身利益。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯在發言中表示，各國必須保護電訊基礎設施，促請美國盟友保持警惕，避免使用華為及其他中國電訊製造商的設備，美方亦將阻止任何損害其通信技術或國家安全系統的形式。<br />\n<br />\n楊潔篪發言時反駁彭斯，指中國法律並無要求公司設置後門程序收集情報，美方的指控只是出於自身利益，歐洲國家不用理會。楊指，華為正與歐洲有緊密合作，歐洲清楚哪條才是讓他們繼續前進的明智道路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190216/s00005/1550329381534/%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E3%80%91%E5%BD%AD%E6%96%AF%E6%8C%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA5g%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%94%E7%AF%AA%E5%8D%B3%E5%A0%B4%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190216%2Fs00005%2F1550329381534%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E6%2596%25AF%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA5g%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599%25E6%25A7%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2584%2585-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%2594%25E7%25AF%25AA%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25A7%2581&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L1u%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=ecad61d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%2